title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
